   INTERNET-PHONES (Undated) _ As it halts decades of investing in
the traditional gear that makes up most of the global telephone
system _ AT&AMP;T is starting to retool its network around a new
generation of technologies inspired by the Internet. For consumers,
this evolution could lead to lower prices. And in the future, as
the new technologies expand from the core of the network to homes
and businesses, consumers could also benefit from new sorts of
features and services. A news analysis by Seth Schiesel.
</P>
