<HEADLINE>
IT'S (AT)786. DO YOU KNOW WHERE YOUR COMPUTER IS? 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (editors: replace (AT) with the typographical symbol)  
 (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By AMY HARMON   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   When computer consultant Gustavo Carreno received an e-mail
message at his Lisbon office last week asking for an appointment to
