<HEADLINE>
CLINTON'S FOREIGN POLICY LACKS COHERENCE, BUT SO DOES THE WORLD 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By DAVID E. SANGER   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ In the space of a week, Secretary of State
