<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS: The N.Y. Times Photo Service has moved the following
photo package to accompany your stories about Joe DiMaggio.
DiMaggio died Monday after a long battle with lung cancer. He was
84.
</P>
<P>
   Photo clients will automatically receive these photos via AP's
PhotoExpress or may download them from either the Wieck Photo
Database in Dallas at 972-392-0888 or from NYTPhotos on Newscom at
305-448-8411. Non-clients can make individual purchases by calling
888-603-1036 or 212-556-4204 or our Photo Sales department at
212-556-1243.
</P>
<P>
   (NYT8) HOLLYWOOD, Fla. -- March 8, 1999 -- OBIT-DIMAGGIO-7,
03-08 whose 56-game hitting streak is of baseball's greatest
records, died at his home Monday in Hollywood, Fla. He was 84.
(Fred R. Conrad/The New York Times)
</P>
