Southampton describes how the trailing edge of owl feathers help to
muffle the sound of the bird's flight. By Charles Seife. 500 words.
(slugged: BC-MILITARY-TIPS-FROM-OWLS-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF) &QL;
