Education Secretary and Tennessee Gov. Lamar Alexander will
announce on Tuesday his second bid for the GOP presidential
nomination. In an interview, Alexander reveals his strategy for
breaking away from the GOP pack and countering his image as a
perennial candidate with no chance of success. By DAN FREEDMAN.
</P>
