the trash hauling business, is acquiring No. 2 Browning-Ferris
Industries of Houston, and taking it to Scottsdale, Ariz. The deal
is worth about $9.1 billion. Allied is a younger, leaner company
that was started in Houston. By NELSON ANTOSH.
