<HEADLINE>
CITING RACIAL IMPACT, JUDGE DISCARDS NCAA TEST-SCORE RULE 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: This is a late add to page 1 of the New York Times.)  
 (DUPLICATION WARNING: The following story is also being sent with
an ``s'' category code.) 
 (lh) 
 By JOE DRAPE   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   A U.S. District Court in Philadelphia on Monday discarded the
National Collegiate Athletic Association's minimum test score
